== [[Wikijunior|Wikijunior]] World War II ==

<span style="font-size: 120%; line-height: 1.5">
This [[wikijunior]] book is on the topic of 'World War II' with the target audience being those who are 10–12 years old. The project will cover significant events, the technology that was used, and some important people who were involved. There will be a main introduction and modules for each specific topic; there will also be a glossary. The project may also include other general interest articles about the war. If you would like more information about contributing, please [[/Contributing/|see here]]. If you would like to have formal credit for being an author, please add your name to the [[/Authors/|authors list]].
</span>

