Is there a way to say Esperanto in German? Just curious. -Drury

: Of course there is. Esperanto is very big in Germany. The word is simply "Esperanto" (with a German pronunciation, not too far from the Esperanto pronunciation of the word). [[User:Junesun|Junesun]] 06:00, 3 July 2007 (UTC)

