==Notes for use==
For all of these templates, you'll have to use html markup to insert lists. Wikimarkup won't render properly. I'm trying to get it fixed.

More info on html lists: [[m:Help:List]]

=='''[[Template:FA Regional Note]]'''==
{{FA Regional Note|To call this template, use: {{tlx|FA Regional Note|text for the note goes here}}}}
This is going to be used for bringing attention to region or country-specific info. For example, when we talk about calling EMS, it might be noted that it's 911 in N. America, but ___ elsewhere, and may not be available at all in some areas.

===[[Template:FA Regional Note Left]]===
